From:

Cc 
<AAcosta@usa.doj.gov> 
Subject: Epstein - Addendum and Letter to Judge Davis 
Date: Wed, 24 Oct 2007 19:45:10 +0000 
Importance: Normal 
Attachments: Addendum.wpd; 071015_Special_Master_Letter4.wpd 
"Acosta, Alex (USAFLS)" 
Jay, 
Pursuant to our conversation, here is the revised letter and a new addendum. The only change to the addendum is that I 
renumbered the new paragraphs from A,B, and C to 7A, 7B, and 7C. Once you approve, I will contact Judge Davis and send 
him the letter. Please execute the addendum, PDF the executed original to me as soon as possible and Fed Ex the original 
to me thereafter. 
EFTA00013518
